## CQRS Flow Diagram

**Command Query Responsibility Segregation**

### Command Side (PostgreSQL)
- **Optimized for writes**
- Real-time operations
- Spatial calculations
- Sub-millisecond response
- ACID transactions

### Query Side (Apache AGE)
- **Optimized for reads**
- Deep graph queries
- 50-hop lineage in 10ms
- Provenance tracking
- Metacognition

### Async Sync
- LISTEN/NOTIFY mechanism
- Zero operational overhead
- Eventual consistency
- Independent scaling

### AI Layer
- In-database ML
- NumPy SIMD (AVX-512)
- Optional GPU (CuPy)
- No external APIs
